    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink9-kilavi">
        <p type="edition"> ituvumatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink9">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> vāḻi yātaṉ vāḻi yaviṉi</l>
          <l> naṉṟuperitu ciṟakka tītil lākuka</l>
          <l> veṉavēṭ ṭōḷē yāyē yāmē</l>
          <l> kayalār nārai pōrviṟ cēkkun</l>
          <l> taṇṭuṟai yūraṉ kēṇmai </l>
          <l> yampalā kaṟka veṉavēṭ ṭēmē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l> 'May Ātaṉ prosper, may Aviṉi prosper.</l>
          <l> Let what is good greatly prevail, let what is bad be nought,'</l>
          <l> thus wants our mother. We,</l>
          <l> 'The intimacy with the man from the village by the cool ghat,</l>
          <l> where cranes full of carp rest on heaps:</l>
          <l> let it not become gossip,' thus we want.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
